{"tid":1586613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"畜膿同防暴推進個陣仆街！！","createTime":"2019-09-22T04:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T05:05:06.000Z","uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"79c9dd904b1387cb885990a3c5e76047cca7d22d","tid":1586613,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:51:25.000Z","msg":"之前成日都討論點樣令班狗真係仆街，於是就開始用水用洗潔精⋯⋯效果好似無乜！倒電油又好易teamkill<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果佢地踩波車呢？成地都係波，跑又要睇路，踩中又仆街？？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FagNPcM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFagNPcM.jpg&h=8936503f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KrzS0jr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrzS0jr.jpg&h=e17d7c54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z9meucN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ9meucN.jpg&h=fe8936e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFJDVSO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFJDVSO.jpg&h=f5fa58b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n足球撚表示可以直接大腳射埋去又得，放到佢地前面又得，距離好易控制！雖然無傷害，但量大就可以做到真正路障，求討論"},{"pid":"8ee013b4fc7f392a12b7c7f551cf2c67ad8bc11e","tid":1586613,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:53:00.000Z","msg":"咁多個波 不如直接同佢哋玩閃避球?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59c6e27ad8a12eb89321919936eed8fb1bf59f3","tid":1586613,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ee013b4fc7f392a12b7c7f551cf2c67ad8bc11e","tid":1586613,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:53:00.000Z","msg":"咁多個波 不如直接同佢哋玩閃避球?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:54:06.000Z","msg":"比佢地射咁點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大量2號足球+魔法點睇"},{"pid":"df956e337d69732ee62009e003a4726667b4